```
I don&#39;t use bootstrap, but I guess the mark-up above would be turned into a submit button, *if* that&#39;s the case, you could add the `name=&quot;register 2&quot;` attribute to it as follows

```
&lt;div class=&quot;submit-btn-area&quot;&gt;
